snippet: The 1996 Olympic gold medalist and WWE professional wrestling star Kurt Angle pulled out of next week’s United States Olympic team trials in Iowa.
abstract: Kurt Angle, 1996 Olympic gold medalist and WWE professional wrestling star, pulls out of United States Olympic wrestling trials because of hamstring and knee injuries.
lead_paragraph: The 1996 Olympic gold medalist and WWE professional wrestling star Kurt Angle pulled out of next week’s United States Olympic team trials in Iowa.
